      "x": 48,
      "y": 113,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 24,
      "text": "Pattern 1: LLM Only",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "fontStyle": "bold",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p1-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#9775fa",
      "backgroundColor": "#f3f0ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "p1-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 175,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "1. System prompt\n\n2. History → messages\n\n3. llm.ainvoke(messages)\n\n4. yield response\n\n————\n✅ Creative output\n✅ No external data\n⚠ Costs tokens\n⚠ Non-deterministic",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p1-example",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 48,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "📦 Packing List Agent",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#9775fa",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p2-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 280,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 50,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "p2-header-label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 288,
      "y": 106,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 38,
      "text": "Pattern 2: LLM +\nAgentic Tool Loop",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "fontStyle": "bold",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p2-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 280,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#9775fa",
      "backgroundColor": "#f3f0ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "p2-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 290,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 240,
      "text": "1. Fetch MCP tools by tag\n\n2. llm.bind_tools()\n\n3. Loop (max 5):\n   a. llm.ainvoke()\n   b. if tool_calls:\n      → call MCP\n      → inject result\n   c. else: done\n\n————\n✅ Live data + reasoning\n⚠ Multiple LLM calls\n⚠ Non-deterministic",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p2-example",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 288,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "⛅ Weather & Activity Agent",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#9775fa",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-header",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 520,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 50,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-header-label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 528,
      "y": 113,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 24,
      "text": "Pattern 3: MCP Direct",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "fontStyle": "bold",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 520,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 1,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 175,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "1. Parse input\n   (keyword matching)\n\n2. Call MCP tool\n   (hardcoded name)\n\n3. Format result\n\n4. yield response\n\n————\n✅ Zero tokens\n✅ Deterministic\n✅ Fast (<100ms)\n✅ Fully testable",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "p3-example",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 528,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "📍 Local Tips Agent",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "rule",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 490,
      "width": 680,
      "height": 30,
      "text": "💡 Rule of thumb: Start with Pattern 3. Only reach for LLM when the task genuinely needs language reasoning.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "fontStyle": "italic",
